    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition and represents a dependable, well-maintained used car that is ready for its next owner. The exterior shows the typical signs of normal use \u2014 you'll notice some light surface scratches and minor scuffs consistent with everyday driving, but there are no significant dents or structural concerns. The paint retains good overall color and gloss. The interior is clean and functional, with the upholstery showing moderate wear on the driver's seat and some light fading on high-contact surfaces, but no tears or major damage. All primary controls, electronics, and comfort features are in working order. Mechanically, the car has been regularly serviced and runs reliably \u2014 the engine starts smoothly, the transmission shifts properly, and the brakes feel responsive. Tires have reasonable tread remaining. This is an honest, solid used car that will serve its next owner well with continued routine maintenance.",
      "price": 35500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed at $32,000, a price that honestly reflects its good overall condition. The exterior presents well \u2014 you'll notice only minor surface scratches consistent with normal everyday use, with no significant dents or major paint damage. The body panels are straight and the paint retains good color and gloss. Mechanically, the car runs reliably and has been maintained appropriately; expect normal wear on components like brakes and tires but nothing that requires immediate major attention. The interior is clean and functional, showing modest signs of use \u2014 think light wear on seat fabric and minor scuffs on trim pieces, but nothing that detracts significantly from comfort or appearance. All major systems \u2014 engine, transmission, HVAC, and electronics \u2014 are in working order. This is a solid, dependable vehicle that has been used but well cared for, and it represents good value for a buyer looking for a reliable car without paying mint-condition prices.",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly to reflect its true current condition \u2014 it is in poor shape and is best suited for a buyer looking for a project car, parts vehicle, or someone with the skills and resources to undertake significant repairs. The exterior shows substantial wear: the paint is heavily faded and oxidized in multiple areas, with deep scratches, visible rust spots, and body panel damage that goes beyond cosmetic concerns. The interior is similarly worn, with torn upholstery, cracked dashboard components, and signs of prolonged use without significant maintenance or care. Mechanically, the vehicle has known issues and should not be expected to perform reliably without investment in repairs \u2014 a pre-purchase inspection by a qualified mechanic is strongly recommended before committing. We are pricing this vehicle accordingly to reflect its condition honestly, and we encourage buyers to factor in potential repair costs when evaluating this listing. What you see is what you get \u2014 no surprises.",
